          <article class="post-type-landing_page" id="article">
            		<div class="intro-text">

      
      
  
      <p class="_subtitle">Contact Us</p>
  
  <h3><strong>Where is the office located?</strong></h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The Office of Scholarships is located within the Office of Student Financial Aid, in Suite 1800 of the Student Services Building (SSB). The Student Services Building is located at 1200 West Harrison Street (near the intersection at Racine).</p>
<h3><strong>What are the office hours?</strong></h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Generally, the office is open 9:00am-5:00pm, Monday through Friday. The office is open during the summer.</p>


</div>
    
		<div class="components">
      
      

